oads/2023/07/virtual_idol_jkt48v_unveiled_as_akb48_group_first_idol_vtuber.jpg" alt="JKT48发布虚拟偶像“JKT48V” AKB48集团首位偶像VTuber" class="wp-image-98030"/><figcaption class="wp-element-caption"> JKT48V：Kanaria Asa/Pia Meraleo/Tana Nona 图片来源：YouTube<br> © 2023 JKT48 运营团队（PT. Indonesia Musik Nusantara） </figcaption></figure><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><div class="youtube"><iframe title="JKT48V公告预告片" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/4atpTUNhz8M?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></div></div></figure><p></p><div class="zhmvw64c8fa0774d3b" ><script async src="https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-3186024119059876"
